CustomField.description: Enter the guidance Distribution provided in relation to the facility margin (midpoint of range). If Variable: input total margin in % above the applicable base rate quoted to client. If below, input with minus symbol. If Fixed: input all-in fixed rate in %. If Preference Share: input the applicable % of Prime as quoted to client. If Insurance: Weighted Average insurance premium in % SGPRT-624
